### 🟢 Register a New User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 🟢 Login User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Authorization: Bearer <eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY3ZTA1Y2U3N2RjZDI2ZjE4YTQzYTU0YSIsImlhdCI6MTc0Mjc1NzA5NSwiZXhwIjoxNzQzMzYxODk1fQ.f-uqqiEM0ZU1Kd77nCDF-xY79tqZWvYgw-rgqZB49pc>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 🟡 Copy Token from Login Response
# After login, copy the token returned from response and use it in next APIs as:
# Authorization: Bearer <eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY3ZTA1Y2U3N2RjZDI2ZjE4YTQzYTU0YSIsImlhdCI6MTc0Mjc1NzA5NSwiZXhwIjoxNzQzMzYxODk1fQ.f-uqqiEM0ZU1Kd77nCDF-xY79tqZWvYgw-rgqZB49pc>
